data.description: NOW OFFERING 15K SELLER CREDIT! Don’t miss this opportunity to own in Todd Creek Vistas! It is move-in ready with lots of character! This home offers the ideal blend of space, style, and functionality.This amazing home sits on 1.5 acres of land that has incredible landscaping, gas fire pit and a lovely outdoor entertainment area for all your friends and family. As you enter the home you are greeted on the main level with an open concept living room and dining room that leads into a gorgeous entertainer's dream kitchen. The kitchen is an entertainer's delight with a large island, upgraded quartz countertops including all new appliances, 6 burner dual fuel range combo with a 36” vented range hood. Every single detail of this house is high-end from the BRAND NEW Driveway! Fully owned 23 solar panels installed January 2022. On average produces 1.2 MWH per month. Level 2 ChargePoint EV car charger. All new paint, blinds, and luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the home. Home has been updated with smart features such as; smart light switches, smart thermostat, video doorbell, hardwired exterior security cameras, smart toilets, Wi-Fi deadbolt, and new smart garage door opener. Home also features a whole home Aquasana water filter system. The home features bidets, that reduce waste and keep septic system healthy. Upper level features the master suite that won't disappoint with a gorgeous fully updated en suite 5piece bathroom. There’s an additional two bedrooms and full size bathroom upstairs as well! On the lower level you will find the fourth bedroom, half bathroom and additional living space for entertainment or relaxation by the cozy fireplace. This home is boasting with space! Not to mention the unfinished walk-out basement that gives you even more room to grow and make it your own! This home has it all in a prime location just minutes to Brighton and Thornton a few miles from Denver Premium Outlets, restaurants, Top Golf, parks, trails, recreation centers and more!
